metadata.name: Fikka NFT
metadata.description:
Fikka Marketplace is your own unique upcoming NFT marketplace to cater a secure, versatile & user friendly NFT marketplace for the Web3 community in order to learn, grow and earn together. We believe in Community growth and elevation of artists and collectors jointly in one ecosystem.


This Fikka NFTs collection is part of an IDO in which we are offering 2% Tokens out of the total 10 Billion Tokens in this Fikka NFTs Presale raising 200k USD, with each Fikka NFT priced at 20$. There will be 10k NFTs in total which will be put on sale on different platforms/chains. Out of 10k total Fikka NFTs, we are offering 6667 NFTs on ETH and 3333 NFTs being offered on Tezos. These 6667 Fikka NFTs collection is launched here against which we are offering Fikka Tokens.

Each 20$ Fikka NFT will be worth 20k Fikka Tokens (FIKKA) + another 25% in Bonus for early investors, making it 25,000 Fikka Tokens (FIKKA) in Total.

The following utilities will be given to the Fikka NFT holders :                                                                                    

Each Fikka NFT holder will get early access to Beta version launch of the Fikka Marketplace.

Artist spotlight every week will be conducted by the Marketplace to ensure excess visibility.                              

Fikka NFT holders will get slots from our future IDO launches.                                                                                  

Specifically for Artists who hold the Fikka NFT will get whitelist spots in future NFT projects in the Fikka Marketplace.

Monthly competitions or raffles will be conducted by the Fikka Marketplace and top 5 artworks will be collected from the Fikka NFT holders.

Each Fikka NFT holder artworks will be featured in the homepage of the Fikka Marketplace for promotion and marketing.
